{"tid":665656,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"議陣投訴何君堯漏報囤地","createTime":"2018-05-15T06:55:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-15T12:37:04.000Z","uid":25558,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"bbd598d14d66a0912ff3f10d015ca60096dbb83f","tid":665656,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T06:55:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180515/20391379\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180515%2F20391379&d=oxW6gKhhKw4scgCLfX8DVGxr1Wzy5cvmMlqj7aCMUDs%3D&h=839720ac\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180515%2F20391379&h=28b6cff8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180515/20391379</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年05月15日 <br />\n<br />\n議陣投訴何君堯漏報囤地<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180515/large/18710829.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180515%2Flarge%2F18710829.jpg&h=96c5d3e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n何君堯<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】立法會議員何君堯早前被揭其家族公司持有粉嶺高球場旁農地，但於有關收回粉嶺高球場動議中發言及投反對票，事前均未有申報利益，議會陣線立法會議員區諾軒及范國威稱，他們已去信議員個人利益監察委員會投訴，要求跟進何未有申報利益。<br />\n<br />\n區諾軒、范國威、陳志全及毛孟靜等議會陣線成員昨日見記者，表示已就何君堯在辯論有關收回粉嶺高爾夫球場動議發言及投反對票時，未有申報其家族公司擁有粉嶺高爾夫球場旁約12萬呎農地，以及早前何被揭涉嫌漏報以離岸公司名義持有深水埗舊式唐樓單位，並接受恒基兆業高價收購等事，去信議員個人利益監察委員會投訴。<br />\n<br />\n區認為議員在立會經常討論不同議題，何在交易中與恒基有物業買賣，有責任事先申報，而何不斷被揭發與討論項目有利益衝突則屬於隱瞞市民。身兼議員個人利益監察委員會副主席的毛孟靜表示，委員會將於月底開會，到時焦點會放在事件是否涉及何刻意隱瞞，以及他是否從中得到利益。<br />\n<br />\n■記者林俊謙  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n何俊仁：坐監都會嗌結束一黨專政<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n爆相爆片"},{"pid":"912ce12dd35f3cab18197b322033fa7ab7bb530c","tid":665656,"uid":3457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T07:12:32.000Z","msg":"依條撚屌好似有免死金牌咁"},{"pid":"9354d5fd8571048b5c4cfe84668f27e6d7a95ae9","tid":665656,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T07:13:56.000Z","msg":"呢鋪都仲有佢不了了知香港人是咪要...."},{"pid":"8b6861ead466e49585e4e1a9ee24dd4ee3d3eb32","tid":665656,"uid":77196,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T07:15:59.000Z","msg":"又煽動犯案又利益衝突，共狗為咗保個垃圾可以去到幾盡 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f1200ebc24b20731abe43369dc9ff467439bc61","tid":665656,"uid":4241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T07:18:54.000Z","msg":"推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a00cc698cb1f2422ddc56eb555de2a1296e4fce","tid":665656,"uid":34223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T12:37:04.000Z","msg":"依隻咁嘅蠢鳩..."}]}